1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Peak performance isn't about
discipline. It's about timing.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
You grind through the afternoon. Force yourself
to work when your body says stop.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Elite athletes don't train the same intensity all day. They
peak, rest, peak again. Your brain works the same way.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Work in 90-minute blocks. Take real breaks. Match
your hardest tasks to your highest energy.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Link in bio — free
energy profile in 30 seconds.

